<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>QueueLess | Hospital Queue Management</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <style>
    /* Landing Page Specific Styles */
    .landing {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2d89ef, #36c3f7);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .landing h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .landing p {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .landing a {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: #2d89ef;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    .landing a:hover {
      background: #f0f0f0;
      color: #1b5fa7;
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 50px;
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      width: 250px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    .feature-card i {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="landing">
  <h1><i class="fas fa-hospital"></i> QueueLess</h1>
  <p>Efficient Hospital Queue Management System<br>Reduce Waiting Time. Track Patients. Stay Organized.</p>

  <div>
    <a href="/signup"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Sign Up</a>
    <a href="/login"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login</a>
  </div>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <i class="fas fa-user-nurse"></i>
      <h3>Staff Dashboard</h3>
      <p>Manage patient queue easily and track waiting patients in real-time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
      <h3>Visitor Dashboard</h3>
      <p>Join queue, view your position, and see your previous hospital visits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
      <h3>Save Time</h3>
      <p>Reduce long waits and improve patient experience.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
